## 🧭 User Flow

```
index.php
    │
    ├── signup.php ──────────────────────► products_listing.php
    │                                             │
    └── login.php  ──────────────────────►        │
                                          ┌───────┴────────┐
                                     [role=user]      [role=vendor]
                                          │                │
                                  buyerProfile.php  vendor_dashboard.php
                                          │                │
                               temp_request.php   addProducts.php
                               (submit rental)    editProduct.php
                                                  createCategory.php
                                                  vendorRegistration.php
```

